<h1>Directory of Math Resources</h1>

    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> >
            <a href="/Science">Science</a>  >             <a href="/Science/Math">Math</a>         </p>

<p><p>Math or mathematics is the study of numbers and variables representing numbers to solve everyday problems, learn about the world around us or to be an exercise in logical reasoning. <br><br> Some applications of math are in the areas of finance, physics, sociology, computer programming, fractal music and geometric art.</p></p>

